<h2 class="bold font-l">Hidamari Sketch x Honeycomb</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Hiro and Sae can communicate with each other telepathically. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MindlinkMates" class='trope-example-link'>Mindlink Mates</a></p>
